Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.37,0:01:40.63,text_up,NTP,0,0,0,,好期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.00,0:03:08.09,text_up,NTP,0,0,0,,你们别偷跑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.09,0:03:09.71,text_up,NTP,0,0,0,,照桥同学 和我…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.93,0:04:03.64,text_up,NTP,0,0,0,,居然是高桥组
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.64,0:04:04.44,text_up,NTP,0,0,0,,畜生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.45,0:04:19.28,text_up,NTP,0,0,0,,修学旅行不去算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.47,0:04:42.77,text_up,NTP,0,0,0,,照桥同学为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.07,0:09:17.78,text_up,NTP,0,0,0,,气势 气势 气势…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.10,0:10:01.48,text_up,NTP,0,0,0,,回去有故事好说了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.83,0:11:09.50,text_up,NTP,0,0,0,,只是你那张脸太恶心了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.50,0:11:10.84,text_up,NTP,0,0,0,,你说啥 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.84,0:11:51.79,text_up,NTP,0,0,0,,别吓我嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.21,0:11:53.34,text_up,NTP,0,0,0,,急死了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.60,0:13:47.56,text_up,NTP,0,0,0,,在各位左手边的是万座毛 是冲绳的观光名胜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.81,0:16:58.15,text_up,NTP,0,0,0,,要死要死 会被咬的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.17,0:17:18.75,text_up,NTP,0,0,0,,这老爷子没完没了了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.80,0:18:57.51,text_up,NTP,0,0,0,,咽口水
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.93,0:19:02.60,text_up,NTP,0,0,0,,咽口水
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.12,0:20:02.58,text_up,NTP,0,0,0,,奇了怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.34,0:20:13.13,text_up,NTP,0,0,0,,你好烦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.04,0:20:48.96,text_up,NTP,0,0,0,,请收下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.96,0:20:49.62,text_up,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.62,0:20:50.29,text_up,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.38,0:23:37.51,text_up,NTP,0,0,0,,齐木 「哦呼」一声
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.51,0:23:39.09,text_up,NTP,0,0,0,,我是不会输给小心美的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.09,0:23:41.39,text_up,NTP,0,0,0,,能试吃的东西我会全吃掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.39,0:23:43.39,text_up,NTP,0,0,0,,齐木看见我害羞了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.39,0:23:45.18,text_up,NTP,0,0,0,,我修学旅行的好戏才刚开始
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.18,0:23:46.18,text_up,NTP,0,0,0,,咽口水
